{The bidding has been as shown.   

Partner's double promises 4 cards in at least one of the Majors. You certainly hope it is \Hs. You bid 2\H and partner raises to 3\H.  

Once partner confirms he has the \Hs you can revalue your hand to 17 points. This gives you enough extra to accept partner's invitation. You bid 4\H.}

